  ('elementary-e0adf6cd-moex-00710', 'elementary-e0adf6cd', 'elementary-e0adf6cd-moex-111-f2876bfc', 'sub-elementary-e0adf6cd-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '韋伯（M. Weber）認為社會的衝突基礎略有三方面，其中有關於財產權的部分是下列那一方面的衝突基 礎，而會對教育產生不良的影響？', '["地位", "權力", "階級", "文化"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cf56b931b4aa", "answer_pdf_sha1": "00d7ab252a18", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "504", "s": "0403", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "教育學大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "教育行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-e0adf6cd-moex-00711', 'elementary-e0adf6cd', 'elementary-e0adf6cd-moex-111-f2876bfc', 'sub-elementary-e0adf6cd-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '「依據學習目的，由學生針對實際所要解決的問題，自己去設計和擬訂計畫，以完成有意義的學習活動。」 前述係指下列何種教學法？', '["設計教學法", "協同教學法", "單元教學法", "編序教學法"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cf56b931b4aa", "answer_pdf_sha1": "00d7ab252a18", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "504", "s": "0403", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "教育學大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "教育行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-e0adf6cd-moex-00712', 'elementary-e0adf6cd', 'elementary-e0adf6cd-moex-111-f2876bfc', 'sub-elementary-e0adf6cd-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '合作學習教學法有多種的模式，對合作學習教學法的敘述，下列何項錯誤？', '["在小組成就區分法（STAD）中，是從個人進步分數來看小組的成績", "在小組競賽法（TGT）中，各組能力相近者到同一競賽桌參加測驗", "在拼圖法第二代（Jigsaw Π）中，每一小組負責同一專家主題的學習", "在小組協力教學法（TAI）中，形成性測驗練習由組內同儕交換批閱"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cf56b931b4aa", "answer_pdf_sha1": "00d7ab252a18", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "504", "s": "0403", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "教育學大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "教育行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-e0adf6cd-moex-00713', 'elementary-e0adf6cd', 'elementary-e0adf6cd-moex-111-f2876bfc', 'sub-elementary-e0adf6cd-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '期末時，音樂老師要學生吹奏直笛以作為學期成績之一，吹奏直笛屬於下列何種評量？', '["檔案評量", "動態評量", "安置評量", "實作評量"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cf56b931b4aa", "answer_pdf_sha1": "00d7ab252a18", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "504", "s": "0403", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "教育學大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "教育行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
